<P>Ya, the full document was really good.&nbsp; Would be nice if he would give permission to append it.&nbsp; That way if he won't get bombarded with emails every couple of days.&nbsp; I assume there was a reason he wouldn't post the document on the boards and wanted to email it privatly.</P>
