				More accurate numbers would be:<br><br>Ally 1100 to 2100<br>Warmly 750 to 1099<br>Kindly 500 to 749<br>Amiable 100 to 499<br>Indifferent 0 to 99<br>Apprehensive -100 to -1<br>Dubious -500 to -101<br>Threatening -800 to -501<br>Scowls -2100 to -801<br><br>There's a little uncertainty about the Warmly range due to changes in game about two years ago... some people think it starts at 800 or 850, and might go up to 1149.  Also max-ally is debated... it might be as high as 2300.  But all the numbers I've listed are absolutely correct from -500 to +500.<br><br>There's a whole chat forum full of old info and advice at EQDruids.  There is also a great deal of faction information in Illia's Bestiary at Allakhazam... notably a big post under the Venril Sathir faction.
				
