				<BR>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
<HR>
ElvenWalker wrote:<BR>Scowls -2100 to -801<BR><BR>Oh - I didn't see this one at first. If - that is accurate instead of Skrax's number than that would make the lowest VERIFIED starting faction at neg 2801 so far as my woof elf vs iksar necro faction.<BR><BR>This would also seem to indicate that I could drop from my baseline of neg 2801 all the way down to neg 4801 if I was to kill a lot of iksar on necro faction.<BR>
<HR>
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<P>Again, those numbers were from old (3+ years) parsing logs and are rough estimates that have been debated even then.&nbsp; They are meant as only a sort of guide to give you an idea where you stand.</P>
<P>I will be the first to say they are not exact, but they are close enough for you to guage where you stand and to also re-iterate that while you can con the same message (dubious for example) you can be worlds apart where you stand on a mobs "dubious" list.&nbsp; While you won't get a merchant to sell to you at any "dubious" point, you may get a quest giver to acknowledge you if you are High dubious as opposed to low dubious.</P>
				
								<p><div style="width: 100%; height: 120; overflow: hidden;">
								
							<a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=670542">Brother Skrax Swifttail</a><br><a href="http://www.scriptedlegacy.net/">Stone Fist on Fennin Ro</a><br><a href="http://eqforums.station.sony.com/eq/board/message?board.id=TNZ&message.id=6162">Monk of Happiness</a>
